title: Elisabeth Schwarzkopf
description:
Heres some stuff from tha fantastic diva Elisabeth Schwarzkopf. 
The album called..In Songs You Love ..is a rare, imported vinyl LP i was lucky to aquire. The 2 CD set is from my personal CD collection and not a download from anyone else..so yunz guyz will have something fresh and new.
enjoy.

PS

Anyone else have any other female vocals from LP, you need to rip them and post them.
Join the crusade and preserve the rarities.
